    dc:description "Fig. 6. Variation in oviscape white microtrichosity. A. Scipopus (Scipopus) planus sp. nov. B. Scipopus (Scipopus) belzebul (Schiner, 1868). C. Scipopus (Parascipopus) nigriscapus subgen. et sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10123252/files/figure.png" ;
